&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are seeking an experienced&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Setup CNC Machinist / Operator&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;to support multi-axis machining operations in a fast-paced prototype and production environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is a hands-on role ideal for machinists who enjoy complex parts, tight tolerances, and working closely with engineering teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
