&lt;li&gt;Refine and finalize and the current prototype&#39;s electrical design to support all phases of prototype maturation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Undertake and complete circuit design tasks, generate detailed schematics, and perform component selection aligned with environmental and system requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply detailed tolerancing, design-for-manufacture principles, and thorough documentation across all electrical prototype phases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support PCB layout design and coordinate with external vendors for fabrication and assembly of PCB components.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with the Space Kinetic manufacturing and engineering team to integrate electrical systems into mechanical assemblies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Verify and validate your electrical designs through testing, troubleshooting, debugging, and iteration to improve system reliability and performance.&lt;/li&gt;
