&lt;h4&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Space Kinetic is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Technical Recruiter&lt;/strong&gt; to help build the team that will redefine how humanity operates in space. This individual will manage full-cycle recruiting efforts across technical disciplines including spacecraft systems, avionics, software, GNC, manufacturing, test, production, and mission operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate has experience recruiting engineers or other specialized technical professionals and understands how to source, engage, and close candidates in competitive markets. This role requires strong sourcing ability, technical curiosity, and the ability to manage multiple searches in a fast-paced startup environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Basic Responsibilities:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Full-Cycle Technical Recruiting&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage end-to-end recruiting processes across engineering, manufacturing, production, and operations roles&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop sourcing strategies and build qualified candidate pipelines&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage candidates from initial outreach through offer acceptance and onboarding&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Conduct candidate screens and present qualified candidates to hiring managers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Technical Talent Acquisition&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identify and engage talent from aerospace, defense, robotics, autonomous systems, advanced manufacturing, and adjacent industries&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Build pipelines for systems engineering, flight software, avionics, structures, manufacturing, test, and mission operations&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Source passive candidates through LinkedIn Recruiter, referrals, networking, Boolean searches, and direct outreach&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
