&lt;p&gt;Partner with hiring managers to define role requirements and candidate evaluation criteria&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provide regular pipeline updates, market feedback, and candidate insights&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support structured interview processes and timely candidate feedback&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Talent Brand and Recruiting Operations&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Serve as an ambassador for Space Kinetic’s mission, culture, and technology vision&lt;/p&gt;
